Comment: 5,0:02:16.46,0:02:21.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k0}{\k471}お前を　守り抜き
Comment: 5,0:02:21.17,0:02:25.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k0}{\k467}側に居よう　救いたい
